    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Iterable<Labor>, java.util.Collection<Labor>, java.util.List<Labor>, java.util.RandomAccess
    public class LaborDeck
extends java.util.ArrayList<Labor>
    This class provides the deck-building mini-game logic for Labor cards. It is not a model entity, making it easier to develop as it can be more freely altered during the course of a game. It is then fully loaded and processed when the game starts.
